ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: cognition
ⲃⲉⲣⲥⲓⲟⲛ: "1.0.0"
ⲗⲁⲛⲅⲩⲁⲅⲉ: zig
ⲙⲟⲇⲩⲗⲉ: cognition

ⲥⲣⲉⲁⲧⲓⲟⲛ_ⲡⲁⲧⲧⲉⲣⲛ:
  ⲥⲟⲩⲣⲥⲉ: RawSensoryData
  ⲧⲣⲁⲛⲥⲫⲟⲣⲙⲉⲣ: CognitiveProcessing
  ⲣⲉⲥⲩⲗⲧ: CognitiveState

ⲃⲉⲏⲁⲃⲓⲟⲣⲥ:
  - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: perception
    ⲅⲓⲃⲉⲛ: Raw sensory input available
    ⲱⲏⲉⲛ: Process sensory data
    ⲧⲏⲉⲛ: Return processed perception
    ⲧⲉⲥⲧ_ⲥⲁⲥⲉⲥ:
      - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: basic_perception
        ⲓⲛⲡⲩⲧ: {sensory_data: "visual_input", format: "raw"}
        ⲉⲝⲡⲉⲥⲧⲉⲇ: {perception: "processed_visual", confidence: 0.95}

  - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: decision_making
    ⲅⲓⲃⲉⲛ: Cognitive state and goals
    ⲱⲏⲉⲛ: Evaluate options and choose action
    ⲧⲏⲉⲛ: Return optimal decision
    ⲧⲉⲥⲧ_ⲥⲁⲥⲉⲥ:
      - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: simple_decision
        ⲓⲛⲡⲩⲧ: {state: "current_state", goals: ["goal1", "goal2"]}
        ⲉⲝⲡⲉⲥⲧⲉⲇ: {decision: "optimal_action", reasoning: "goal_oriented"}

  - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: self_awareness
    ⲅⲓⲃⲉⲛ: System state and history
    ⲱⲏⲉⲛ: Analyze own performance and state
    ⲧⲏⲉⲛ: Return self-assessment
    ⲧⲉⲥⲧ_ⲥⲁⲥⲉⲥ:
      - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: performance_assessment
        ⲓⲛⲡⲩⲧ: {history: "past_actions", current_state: "system_state"}
        ⲉⲝⲡⲉⲥⲧⲉⲇ: {assessment: "good_performance", improvements: ["area1"]}